MoniMichelle Sports Facility Construction Company CEO, Ebi Egbe, has decried the current state of the Godswill Akpabio Int’l Stadium in Uyo, Akwa Ibom state capital.
Egbe called on the state government to ensure proper maintenance of the world class sports edifice is giving utmost attention.
He also reminded construction giants, Julius Berger, to keep to its previous agreement reached with the Akwa Ibom state government  to maintain the stadium for a period of ten years.
MoniMichelle, an indigenous sports facility construction company recently completed the up-grade of the Enyimba FC Stadium in Aba to international standard.
